#

Oven-Baked Mackerel with Herb Citrus Marinade and Roasted Root Vegetables

$15.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

Fish

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

HealthyGourmetDinnerFish Dish

Description

A delightful dish featuring succulent mackerel infused with citrus herbs, served alongside a medley of roasted root vegetables for a wholesome meal.

Ingredients

  • Mackerel fillets: 4 pieces
  • Lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh parsley: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Fresh dill: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • Garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • Olive oil: 3 tbsp
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • Carrots: 2, chopped
  • Sweet potatoes: 2, chopped
  • Beets: 2, chopped
  • Red onion: 1, sliced
